{"lemma":"ذالٌ","slug":"ذالٌ","root":"#.#.#","root_slug":"_-_-_","root_link":"/words/roots/_-_-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":11},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n13633","n14186","n14220"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B0%D8%A7%D9%84%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"Name of the ninth letter of the Arabic alphabet (ذ (ḏ)), representing the sound /ð/"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to drag (of a garment)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to get a tail, or to have one's tail become long (of an animal)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to raise one's tail (of an animal)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to drag one's garments in arrogance (of a person)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to strut (of a person)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be humiliated, to be despised (of a person)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become humble (of a person or one's condition)"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to become weak and emaciated from ill treatment"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to be pleased"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to make (something) insignificant","tags":["transitive"]}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ðaːl/","/ðaː.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n13633","headword_ar":"ذَاَلَ","root":"*A^l","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aA^alato","text_ar":"ذَاَلَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aA^alaAnN","text_ar":"ذَاَلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aA^olN","text_ar":"ذَاْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aA^alN","text_ar":"ذَاَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (accord. to different copies of the S and K, the latter accord. to the TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. a camel, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walked,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"went, lightly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, T, S:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lightly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quickly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IF,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and proudly, with an inclining of the body from side to side."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IF, K.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daA^ala","text_ar":"دَاَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aA^alaAnN","text_ar":"ذَاَلَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.]"}],"source_refs":["T","K","S","AZ","IF"]},{"entry_id":"n14186","headword_ar":"ذَالٌ","root":"*wl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain letter of the alphabet,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, ISd, K,) ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*","text_ar":"ذ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pronounced with the voice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[not with the breath only,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and always a radical, not a substitute for another letter, nor augmentative;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(ISd, TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"its place of utterance is at the roots of the teeth, near the place of utterance of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t","text_ar":"ت"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"v","text_ar":"ث"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; and it may be masc. and fem.; (B, TA;) [but generally it is fem.; and therefore] the dim. is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*uwayolapN","text_ar":"ذُوَيْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*owaAlN","text_ar":"اَذْوَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAlaAtN","text_ar":"ذَالَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)       -A2-  Also The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"comb"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a cock. (Kh, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["Lth","ISd","K"]},{"entry_id":"n14220","headword_ar":"ذَالَ","root":"*yl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ya*iylu","text_ar":"يَذِيلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ayolN","text_ar":"ذَيْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a garment)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was long, so that it touched the ground."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, had a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ayol","text_ar":"ذَيْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"; [app. said of a horse &c., as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had a long tail,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a pendent portion to his tail;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and probably of a garment, as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it had a skirt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower extremity, reaching nearly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quite, to the ground,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dragged upon the ground, when made to hang down;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and perhaps of a man, as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he had a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*yl","text_ar":"ذيل"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to his garment;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*oyala","text_ar":"اَذْيَلَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M, K.) ―         -b3-  And, said of a man, (M, Msb, K,) aor. as above, (M, Msb,) and so the inf. n., (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He walked with an elegant and a proud and self-conceited gait, dragging his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ayol","text_ar":"ذَيْل"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skirt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the lower extremity of his garment"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (M, K;) and in like manner"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAlato","text_ar":"ذَالَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said of a she-camel: (M:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he dragged his"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*oyaAl","text_ar":"اَذْيَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skirts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the lower extremities of his garment"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garments"},{"kind":"text","text":"],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by reason of pride and self-conceit:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAlato","text_ar":"ذَالَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S,)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY mi$oyatihaA","text_ar":"فِى مِشْيَتِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a girl, or young woman, (T,) or of a woman, (S,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ta*iylu","text_ar":"تَذِيلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S,) inf. n. as above, (T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"she dragged her"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^a*oyaAl","text_ar":"اَذْيَال"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"her"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*ayol","text_ar":"ذَيْل"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upon the ground, walking with an elegant and a proud and self-conceited gait."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S.) [See also 5.] ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*Al bi*anabihi","text_ar":"ذال بِذَنَبِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He raised his tail;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K;) said of a horse, and of a mountaingoat. (M.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*Alt bi*anabihaA","text_ar":"ذالت بِذَنَبِهَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a camel)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spread her tail upon her thighs."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*Al","text_ar":"ذال"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_ilayohi","text_ar":"اـِلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AinobasaTa","text_ar":"اِنْبَسَطَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acted towards him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"behaved to him, with boldness, forwardness, presumptuousness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arrogance"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t*y~l","text_ar":"تذيّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*Al Al$~aYo'u","text_ar":"ذال الشَّىْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, Msb, K,) aor. as above, (M,) and so the inf. n., (Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The thing was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, low, base, vile, mean, contemptible,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ignominious."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*Alt HaAluhu","text_ar":"ذالت حَالُهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His state,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"condition, became lowered,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abased;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"t*Aylt","text_ar":"تذايلت","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*Alt","text_ar":"ذالت"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a woman, (M, K,) and of a she-camel, (M,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, lean,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"emaciated,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and in a bad condition."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M.)"}],"source_refs":["M","Msb","K","T","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}